{"tid":718943,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日111巴士上跌左野","createTime":"2018-06-27T05:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T05:32:00.000Z","uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc737a66ab0c7f1c1bb0c6d395f2f6950c207e26","tid":718943,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"唔知開咩台 但係學生八達通就放係校園台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 琴日係紅磡上左往坪石既111巴士 上左冇耐先見倒地下有個八達通套 但唔知係我上之前已經係度定我上後先跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我望過入面除左學生八達通冇其他野 我望過下有冇類似相既學生/人但唔覺有 我就交左比司機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/132947_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F132947_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=103d60c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你應該認得自己個咁特別既套 快啲去攞返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}